snippet.title: To Azimuth - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the first trailer for the new game from [bracket]games, To Azimuth, best described as an alien abduction mystery adventure game (mostly) set in 1970s Alabama.

Help fundthis game now on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1978921498/to-azimuth
Vote for To Azimuth on Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=341794803
